verbose_text: C-SERT-siRNA treatment (30 mug day -1, 7-day) doubled basal extracellular 5-HT levels in the CPu versus PBS treated mice (9.9 +/-1.6 and 4.7 +/-0.7 fmol fraction -1, respectively; n = 7-8; P < 0.01) and provoked a lesser response of the SSRI citalopram to increase extracellular 5-HT (XREF_FIG).
